From the Infowars web site ::

On this Friday edition of the Alex Jones Show, coverage of Bilderberg 2011 continues. Paul Joseph Watson and Aaron Dykes report the latest developments from St. Moritz, Switzerland, where the globalist cabal is holding its annual confab and where the elite are hammering out their agenda for the next year. Alex talks with intrepid Bilderberg sleuth and journalist Jim Tucker and also AFP editor Mark Anderson. Regular Friday guest Bob Chapman of the International Forecaster newsletter joins Alex to provide his insight on the globalists and matters economic.
